            "text_XeFXQe": {
              "type": "text",
              "name": "t:names.text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>To enhance accessibility, our website includes (or is working toward):</p><ul><li>Text alternatives (alt text) for images and non-text elements</li><li>Clear color contrast between text and backgrounds</li><li>Keyboard-friendly navigation</li><li>Descriptive link text and form labels</li><li>Consistent page structure and headings</li><li>Compatibility with modern screen readers and assistive technologies</li></ul><p>We regularly review our site to identify and address potential accessibility issues.</p>",
